00:59:22.020 --> 00:59:25.400 align:middle line:84%
We don't need to
make a global event.

00:59:25.400 --> 00:59:27.570 align:middle line:90%
We can make individual gestures.

00:59:27.570 --> 00:59:30.260 align:middle line:10%
And I think my
feeling, my sense,

00:59:30.260 --> 00:59:32.190 align:middle line:10%
is that the world
is going to change

00:59:32.190 --> 00:59:36.620 align:middle line:10%
through thousands and then
millions of individual gestures

00:59:36.620 --> 00:59:39.510 align:middle line:10%
